					html: '<p>The triple camera system on the back is good too, combining a 48MP main, a 16MP ultra-wide angle and an 8MP telephoto camera. New for the 7T Pro is a super-macro mode, which is surprisingly good, producing crisp images up to just 2.5cm from the lens â€“ great fun. The 7T Pro canâ€™t quite beat the <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/technology/iphone" data-component="auto-linked-tag">iPhone</a> 11 Pro or Pixel 4XL, but it matches or beats the rest on detail and utility.</p>',
